author: max
name: ForwardDeleter
install_msg:
Thanks for installing.
This cog relies on red's autoimmune, to ignore role(s) or user(s) use `[p]autoimmune` from red. You are not immune from any of the forwarded messages without setting up autoimmune.
<https://docs.maxapp.tv/docs/forwarddeleter.html> for documentation.
If you enjoy my work, you can donate at [buymeacoffee](<https://buymeacoffee.com/ltzmax>)
description: A cog that deletes forwarded messages and allows them in specified channels.
short: A cog that deletes forwarded messages and allows them in specified channels.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any End User Data.
